fields.description:
h3. Steps to Reproduce
OS X 10.8.5, SDK 3.2.2, Titanium Studio 3.2.1

Tried to build and run the app on a Samsung device.

Returns the following error:

Failed to install apk on 88b23ce0
Application Installer abnormal process termination.  Process exit value was 143
Application Installer abnormal process termination.  Process exit value was 143

h3. Actual Result
Failed to install apk on 88b23ce0
Application Installer abnormal process termination.  Process exit value was 143
Application Installer abnormal process termination.  Process exit value was 143

h3. Expected Result
Installation of app on Samsung device.

comments.body: Can you please run the application and attach the console log to investigate further?
This is happening on my Galaxy S2.
